Tuition Bonus Program
When we started the $15,000 Tuition Bonus program a year ago we were asked if that was "real money" or just fluff. Today Robert and Jerzy can attest it's truly real money!
It's a simple program for our student drivers - $125/month bonus for 5 years and then a $7500 check on your 5 year anniversary. Once you've paid off your tuition, the rest goes in your pocket!
We have more and more professional drivers hitting this milestone each month!  Congratulations! Click here to see pictures of past recipients.










Gary Helms makes America’s Road Team
Gary Helms, master trainer at Covenant Transport, was named to the American Trucking Associations' 2017-2018 America's Road Team. 




Covenant named a 2016 Top 100 Trucker
Pointing to crucial factors in providing on-time and reliable service to shippers, editors at Inbound Logistics magazine have named Covenant Transport a 2016 Top 100 Trucker -- a leader in innovation and customer service, capable of meeting the ever-changing demands of the freight market. 




Covenant named a top carrier by Logistics Management magazine
Tyson Wimberly, senior vice president of sales at Covenant Transport, pictured right, accepts a 2016 Quest for Quality award, following Covenant's being named a top dry freight carrier nationally by Logistics Management magazine. 







