Experienced Drivers
NOW HIRING EXPERIENCED OTR COMPANY TRUCK DRIVERS WHO WANT TO EARN MORE MONEY!
MAKE 52-56¢ PER MILE AS PART OF A TEAM!
With two drivers on board, a Covenant Transport truck can help you make a lot more money for your miles!
NO PARTNER?!? No problem. We’ll match you up when you get here with a compatible partner of your choice.
No HAZMAT?!? No problem. We’ll pay for it for you when you get here
If you are an experienced, professional CDL-A holder who wants to get paid more, we have excellent OTR driving opportunities open now that can help you do just that! You can give yourself a pay raise and get more miles without driving more.
        
Split the miles with a driving partner and you can earn more per mile. That’s right! You can make more money as part of a driving team at Covenant than a solo driver with your current carrier.
PLUS… $1000/WK Minimum GUARANTEE when driving on a Haz-Mat Team.





