Orientation
COVENANT TRANSPORT HAS AN EASY, COMFORTABLE ORIENTATION PROCESS TO GET YOU IN AND BACK OUT ON THE ROAD EARNING QUICKLY.
We provide free transportation, lodging and meals while you’re learning about our opportunities and meeting other potential driving partners. Orientation is an ideal time to connect with other truck drivers who would make a great partner and get you on the road to earning more money for your miles.
We have three convenient locations for you to get the essential training you need to get on the road as quickly as possible:

Pomona, CA
Chattanooga, TN
Hutchins, TX

Click here to see a list of items you need to bring with you to Orientation
WE HIRE FROM ALL 48 STATES!






