Description


Reviews (0)



Product Description
Covenant Transportation  Group Profile and Analysis
Downloadable report
 
In this profile report, we review Covenant Transportation Group.  Covenant  Transportation Group is a $674 million transportation services company.  The company provides truckload services and logistics (brokerage) services to its many customers.  A comprehensive review is conducted of the company and presented in this report.
A company overview summarizing the company’s lines of business is provided.  An in-depth profile of the executive team and board of directors is provided along with an organizational chart of the senior executive staff.  The report provides information on the geographic areas the company serves. In the business overview, the company’s terminal locations are listed, along with a chart depicting the acquisition history.  A revenue comparison is done between revenues today and 10 years ago. Annual revenue growth is highlighted for the last 5 years. Net income is compared to 2003 and 2012. Net income is presented for the last 5 years. A  review of the revenue mix is presented
A business overview is provided with an in-depth review of each line of business: truckload and solutions.   A look at the operating statistics is provided for the last five years for truckload and two years for solutions.  A review of the competitors by each business line is also provided in the report. In addition, a SWOT analysis is done on the company with strengths, weaknesses, opportunities and threats highlighted.
Press release highlights are included in the report for the last two years capturing major announcements or changes that the company has publically announced.  Information on the company’s information systems is provided.
Last, two years of financial information is provided for review that highlight revenue, operating income and operating statistics from 2008 through 2013.
This comprehensive report will provide the reader with a solid overview of Covenant  Transportation and is an invaluable source of knowledge for the reader.
All information in the report is based upon public information.




