	Item 7.01




	Regulation FD Disclosure.





	 



	 


	On January 26, 2017, Covenant Transportation Group, Inc., a Nevada corporation (the "Company"), conducted a conference call for investors and the public at approximately 10:00 a.m. (Eastern), to discuss the Company's previously reported financial and operating results for the quarter and year ended December 31, 2016.  A written transcript of the conference call is attached as Exhibit 99 to this report and incorporated herein by reference.







	 


	 









