About Us
Capacity, Equipment, Solutions...Covenant Transport Solutions provides the answers to your transportation needs.  As a customer, you can utilize our extensive preferred carrier network of small and private fleets, as well as over 3,000 asset tractors within Covenant Transportation Group’s network of companies.  Our in-house 24 hour customer support will prove to be an integral part of your shipping network.”
Benefits

Year round capacity including surge periods 
Equipment for non-standard loads
Reefers, Logistics Vans, Flat Beds, Drop Decks
Concentrated density for your problem lanes


Seamless system integration for added visibility
EDI
Internet-based load tracking


For More information, call 866-398-2884
About CTG
Covenant Transport Solutions is a subsidiary of Covenant Transportation Group, Inc. (CTG).  CTG is a holding company for several transportation subsidiaries that offer premium transportation services for customers throughout the United States, Canada, and Mexico. The Company's Class A common stock is traded on the NASDAQ National Market under the symbol CVTI.  More information is available at www.ctgcompanies.com.
 










 

