          sign this Application. This electronic signature ensures that I am the
           Applicant as provided and identified in the Application, indicates my
            approval of the information, terms and conditions contained in the
            Application, affirms the accuracy of the information provided in the
            Application and serves as my intent to sign. I acknowledge, accept
            and understand that my electronic signature is admissible in court
            and constitutes a written and electronic signature in accordance
            with The Federal Global and National Commerce Act and The Uniform
            Electronic Transactions Act as in effect in any relevant jurisdiction,
            including, without limitation, the state of Kansas. Further,
            by checking this box and pressing submit, I acknowledge that I have
            read and understand the terms and conditions of this Application in
            their entirety.
        






